Open Sea Map Plugin for OpenCPN
=======================================

The purpose of this plugin is to provide a connection between Open Sea Map and OpenCPN. 

The aims are to:

1. View seamarks
2. Caching - and refresh cache
3. And finally full crud operations - Create/Read/Update/Delete


Compiling
=========
You have to be able to compile OpenCPN itself - Get the info at http://opencpn.org/ocpn/developers_manual

* go to the plugin subdirectory in your OpenCPN source tree
* git clone git://github.com/ktec/osm_pi.git

Build as normally:

* cd ..
* cd build
* cmake ..
* cmake --build .

Requires
========

libcurl - http://curl.haxx.se/docs/install.html

